                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17891209-59-off287 t17891209-59-cd288"></join> last, four cloth coats, value 39 s. a silk waistcoat, value 3 s. a cotton waistcoat, value 3 s. a worsted ditto, value 3 s. two pair of corderoy breeches, value 12 s. and a pair of thickset ditto, value 7 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17891209-59-victim584" type="victimName">
                     Bernard 
